video.title: Power Rangers R.P.M.
video.synopsis: The Power Rangers' new member, Dillon, isn't sure he wants to be on the team until he has a dream that sets the Rangers into action.

episodes.synopsis: The Venjix computer network is laying ruin to the entire planet, and the human race has retreated into the environmentally shielded city of Corinth.
episodes.title: The Road to Corinth

episodes.synopsis: As Venjix grows stronger, it becomes clear that the Rangers need more than three operators to defend the city.
episodes.title: Fade to Black

episodes.synopsis: Dillon is faced with the choice of seeking out his past or helping the Rangers as promised.
episodes.title: Rain

episodes.synopsis: When Ziggy must find the new Green Ranger, he finds the perfect candidate in Tenaya 7 -- until he learns she's a machine working for Venjix!
episodes.title: Go for the Green

episodes.synopsis: When Dillon struggles to activate the invincibility mode of his suit, he challenges Dr. K to come out from behind her protective screen.
episodes.title: Handshake

episodes.synopsis: Ziggy's recruitment as Ranger Green is put into question when parts of his shady past are revealed.
episodes.title: Ranger Green

episodes.synopsis: Scott is flooded with memories of his brother when he returns to Marcus' crash site to retrieve a component for the new Megazord configuration.
episodes.title: Ranger Red

episodes.synopsis: Mr. and Mrs. Landsdown suddenly reappear in Summer's life, intent on making their daughter live up to her promise to marry into a wealthy family.
episodes.title: Ranger Yellow: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Diamonds and pretty dresses are no longer important to Summer, who finds her true calling in what she does with the Rangers.
episodes.title: Ranger Yellow: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Flynn's biggest passion is helping people, but his heroics as the Blue Ranger are cut short when there is a malfunction in his suit.
episodes.title: Ranger Blue

episodes.synopsis: While attempting to overcome a power problem with the Rangers' new Zord configuration, Dr. K is haunted by a terrible mistake.
episodes.title: Doctor K

episodes.synopsis: When Venjix sends an attack bot from Dillon's past to infiltrate the city, Dillon is torn between destroying the bot or finding answers to his past.
episodes.title: Blitz

episodes.synopsis: As the Venjix Virus comes closer to taking over Dillon entirely, the other Rangers and Dr. K race to find a way to slow the growth rate of the virus.
episodes.title: Brother's Keeper

episodes.synopsis: Seeking answers to Dillon's past, the Rangers go outside Corinth to a place Dillon thinks he remembers, unaware that it's a trap.
episodes.title: Embodied

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers once again find themselves saved by the Gold and Silver Rangers.
episodes.title: Ghosts

episodes.synopsis: As the Rangers take a more offensive approach against Venjix, the virus traps the citizens of Corinth and proceeds to suck the air out of the city.
episodes.title: In Or Out

episodes.synopsis: Dillon discovers that his sister might be imprisoned in the same factory where Gem and Gemma were once held prisoner by Venjix.
episodes.title: Prisoners

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers learn they must return to the factory and destroy the Venjix Doomsday Box that is being built.
episodes.title: Belly of the Beast

episodes.synopsis: When Gem and Gemma's careless antics nearly lands them caught in a trap, they realize that they must work together as a team with the other Rangers.
episodes.title: Three's a Crowd

episodes.synopsis: In an effort to impress his father, Scott makes a reckless trip out to the wasteland.
episodes.title: Heroes Among Us

episodes.synopsis: With their resources dangerously low, Dr. K has to trust the untested technology of the WheelZord to try to destroy the latest attack bot.
episodes.title: Not So Simple

episodes.synopsis: When an attack bot puts all of Corinth's men to sleep, it's up to the girls to suit up and defend Corinth.
episodes.title: The Dome Dolls

episodes.synopsis: For the first time ever, join Ziggy as he takes you behind the scenes of the Power Rangers.
episodes.title: And' Action

episodes.synopsis: Truman discovers that Dr. K was responsible for creating the Venjix Virus.
episodes.title: Ancient History

episodes.synopsis: When Dillon discovers that the two keys to his watch fit together to play another song, he uses it to try to reach Tenaya 7.
episodes.title: Key to the Past

episodes.synopsis: Dillon is betrayed after he and Tenaya 7 break into the Venjix Palace to retrieve codes that are needed to stop an attack bot.
episodes.title: Beyond a Doubt

episodes.synopsis: Dillon's search for Tenaya is put on hold when Scott is shot with a key that allows Shifter to control him.
episodes.title: Control-Alt-Delete

episodes.synopsis: Ziggy must pay back the $5 million he owes Fresno Bob.
episodes.title: Run Ziggy Run

episodes.synopsis: Ziggy accidentally teleports himself and Dr. K into a cave.
episodes.title: If Venjix Won

episodes.synopsis: Dillon fears the virus will take him over.
episodes.title: End Game

episodes.synopsis: When the magnetic blast goes off and all the electricity goes out in Corinth, Venjix makes his move to take the city.
episodes.title: Danger and Destiny: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers race to insert a virus into Venjix before he takes over Corinth.
episodes.title: Danger and Destiny: Part 2
